{"tid":2498693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大二號橋攻防戰三男一女被控暴動續審  片段顯示警拒和平解決造成衝突","createTime":"2021-04-21T10:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T11:43:49.000Z","uid":56115,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"111171f23cff6e2b056f96d5f12b2c7616378a0d","tid":2498693,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:32:20.000Z","msg":"前年11月警方與示威者在中大二號橋展開攻防戰，其後闖入校園施放催淚彈並制服多人。當中三男一女大專生事後被控暴動及蒙面等罪，案件今續審。控方庭上播放當日傳媒直播片段，顯示有人<span class=\"red\">建議警方後退，惟在場防暴警拒絕，並警告在場人士及記者散開，即使有人出言勸止也不理會。</span><br />\n<br />\n控方播放傳媒片段，其中有線新聞直播片段顯示當天下午2時許有人向警方表示：「大家都唔好衝擊大家。」<span class=\"red\">並建議警員後退。惟警員拒絕</span>，並聲言他們要保持道路和鐵路暢通，以及保護道路使用者的安全，表明如果示威者不離開，他們也不會撤走。<br />\n<br />\n及後鏡頭轉至黑衣人一方，中大新聞與傳播學院專業應用副教授、曾任港台《鏗鏘集》編導的潘達培向示威者複述警方要求。數名黑衣人上前聆聽，當中有人表示不打算衝前，「大家都唔好有動作」。"},{"pid":"966f2b5d060fc88843d1b28a20c0c2bca8d27b82","tid":2498693,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210421/BL7ZA5G4ZVH4LIH4L3ZBUSPR6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210421%2FBL7ZA5G4ZVH4LIH4L3ZBUSPR6Y%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=a622082a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210421%2FBL7ZA5G4ZVH4LIH4L3ZBUSPR6Y%2F&h=17049455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210421/BL7ZA5G4ZVH4LIH4L3ZBUSPR6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"2120608a5e8a67112663742379eaa04f443c4609","tid":2498693,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce4a09504d0ce49a295dbab50f61162f9b33665","tid":2498693,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"控方今傳召高級督察<span class=\"red\">鍾家平</span>，庭上讀出其口供。鍾家平指，案發時他駐守將軍澳雜項調查小隊主管，兼東九龍總區第二梯隊第一小隊指揮官。他稱，當日其小隊被派去中文大學執勤，同行有三隊由一名警長和三名警員組成的<span class=\"red\">「捕捉小隊」。</span><br />\n<br />\n庭上播放多段新聞片段，包括香港 01、有線、蘋果日報。片段顯示，中文大學新聞與傳播學院專業應用副教授潘達培曾與示威者對話。及後有記者和一男一女走向警方，表示「希望傾兩句」。<br />\n<br />\n該兩人向警方傳達示威者訊息，希望警方撤退，並指「可唔可以兩邊都唔好衝」。警方多次強調「唔會離開」，指除非示威者先離開警方才會離開。突然有警員大叫「畀警告啦，舉旗」，對方則大喊「等等！唔係！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-12-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E6%92%AD%E7%89%87%E8%A6%8B%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%8B%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%92%A4%E9%80%80%E9%81%AD%E6%8B%92-%E9%A6%96%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%8A%AC%E8%B5%B7%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-12-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2592%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258B%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%2580%2580%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258B%2592-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258A%25AC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2585%25B3%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=3f63f02f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-12-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2592%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258B%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%2580%2580%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258B%2592-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258A%25AC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2585%25B3%2F&h=9ad0b3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-12-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E6%92%AD%E7%89%87%E8%A6%8B%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%8B%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%92%A4%E9%80%80%E9%81%AD%E6%8B%92-%E9%A6%96%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%8A%AC%E8%B5%B7%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3/</a>"},{"pid":"5c2abb4098cba34feaa5e7a94b1877b1bec491f8","tid":2498693,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"黑警鍾家平<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2935000/2937924/04211_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2935000%2F2937924%2F04211_1024.jpg&h=7f52b70a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40a90cb33d01df70ffd8687a90b4cce504cead33","tid":2498693,"uid":166080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c137cf256d14b7a6340e8bb984ed480cbb52cf4a","tid":2498693,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495fcadbb7677f09d3d6d142f6ae12407c984d68","tid":2498693,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c2abb4098cba34feaa5e7a94b1877b1bec491f8","tid":2498693,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"黑警鍾家平<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2935000/2937924/04211_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2935000%2F2937924%2F04211_1024.jpg&h=7f52b70a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5790bc6ed16f656e0866512aa89c7312659db0","tid":2498693,"ui